MPC

Interface Token

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TokenId, TokenInt, TokenKey, TokenOp, TokenString

    public interface Token
    Interface for all token types contained in the 610 Pascal Compiler. Instances of implementors of this interface represent all tokens found in a Pascal program. The implementors are: TokenId (identifiers), TokenInt (integer literals), TokenKey (keywords, implemented with a table shared with TokenId), TokenOp (operators and punctuation), and TokenString (string literals).
